  Our Take on Challenging AI Questions (Bonus Interview)

This bonus section is an interview between Caleb and Shelby for 'The Curious Refuge Podcast.' In the episode, Caleb and Shelby have an honest conversation about what AI means for the future of creativity.

They answer all of your hot-button questions like, 'Is AI Ethical?' and 'Is AI the end of Hollywood?' while also giving insight into their personal beliefs on the existence of extraterrestrial life...

We hope you enjoy the video. You can also treat this one as a podcast and listen in the background. Enjoy!
